{"tid":2103353,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】遏監獄疫情 加州8,000名囚犯下月底前提早出獄","createTime":"2020-07-11T06:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T06:57:02.000Z","uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c859291d85a9a25b47fc76086df73d8ff6d1f5","tid":2103353,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"節錄：蘋果<br />\n<br />\n由於監獄內爆發武漢肺炎疫情，加州宣佈，多達8,000名囚犯會在8月底之前獲提早釋放，以減輕監獄系統內擠迫情況，阻止疫情再度擴大。州長紐森（Gavin Newsom）早前表示，會加強監獄內的抗疫措施。"},{"pid":"8d193966fead15291d5c1e760f582bb5ab31f15b","tid":2103353,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"提早獲釋的將<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">包括沒有涉及暴力犯罪，或被判囚180天或以下刑期的囚犯。當中4,800名可早於今個月底前獲釋。</span>而在聖昆廷州立監獄（San Quentin State Prison）等幾個出現疫情的監獄服刑的囚犯，刑期在一年或以下、且沒有涉及暴力罪行，也可於8月底前獲釋。此外，身體健康狀況被認為屬感染武漢肺炎「高危」的囚犯亦可獲提早釋放。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecdeb71a0a0447802d7f5df02190c716d1bbd61","tid":2103353,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"疫情期間協助維持監獄安全和秩序的囚犯，減刑12周。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd867aa77961bd3998d853267aaf2afc9176917","tid":2103353,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"無犯咁邊夠人做血汗工廠？"},{"pid":"a5e37c09aa7cdb75d2fa142959e36bc6e56f9273","tid":2103353,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bd867aa77961bd3998d853267aaf2afc9176917","tid":2103353,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"無犯咁邊夠人做血汗工廠？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:51:15.000Z","msg":"美國d犯人要做工廠？"}